lyTime":"2018-03-07T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"號稱好打得既奶媽比圍村佬轟出村之後。就多左人打郊野公園主意。填維港以外又突然好驚環團(但三跑又一鎚定音)"},{"pid":"af2448698fd0c0f9a572ca57fd0714edb5cbf050","tid":582952,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"問題一直唔係係塊地度，而係政策出問題，姐係利益。<br />\n<br />\n依家啲樓價咁貴係源於高地價政策同北水keep住流落黎，<br />\n你以為填咗水塘，剷咗個郊野公園攞晒去起樓就會平？<br />\n<br />\n唔會囉，一日唔改政策一日都唔會跌返去以前既水平<br />\n最多只會放寬按揭成數，降低個入場門檻<br />\n但到時可能講緊d後生為左買樓係揹住4，50年按揭"},{"pid":"f674a57729f6271c91af7b4cdac8a73bc73a2d19","tid":582952,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:14:43.000Z","msg":"咁俄羅斯一定係世界第一強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7698534cc96f029711dd07a203ab5b283ea70403","tid":582952,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"香港算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854b12670481348a2b1ac739a38af0ded228f31a","tid":582952,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲咪叫丢人現眼<br />\n你個腦就真係比正常人少三倍喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"7c4a33474dd48b2da0d67a44ca8b541d026a7a4a","tid":582952,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"弱智到以為開多d地就贏到人地新加坡 <br />\n香港廢就係因為太多弱智仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3165a3d5a09e3b0fa398f668a1c2e61a9c8e459c","tid":582952,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"983828f4b3841d9cf40b67a6a5887eb1da113c67","tid":582952,"uid":44153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0c9dfc5659905f959ee958e4bcccbda04f99c8","tid":582952,"uid":123710,"like":0,"dislike":40,"score":-40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:11:28.000Z","msg":